-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--- Introduction                                                            ---
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This code provides tools for Riemannian shape analysis with second order 
Sobolev metrics on closed plane curves. For details see the paper
  A Numerical Framework for Sobolev Metrics on the Space of Curves
by
  Martin Bauer, Martins Bruveris, Philipp Harms and Jakob Møller-Andersen

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--- Dependecies                                                             ---
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To calculate Karcher means one needs the Manopt library, available at
  www.manopt.org

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--- Usage                                                                   ---
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

See the file
  example.m
for basic examples regarding the usage of the code.

